Package helpers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChannelTreeRetriever
    Fetches RBNB channel names for SegaChannelListServlet.
    DataCollector
    This is a helper class for SegaDataServlet that is used to connect to RBNB.
    DataFetchHelper
    This helper class handles connecting to RBNB, collects the data and wraps it in a custom RBNB object.
    ExperimentParameterObject
    This is a container class used to store unique experiment parameter objects.
    KeyValueObject
    A generic key/value pair object This is only used by SegaDataReqeustFormServlet to return server types and their display names, but this could easily be deleted and XYDataPointObject could be used instead - they are the same class with "x,y" instead of "key,value"
    MySQLHelper
    MySQLHelper
    RBNBChannelObject
    This is a helper class used to store channel information as well as the channel's datapoints and timestamps in an array of XYDataPointObjects
    RBNBSourceObject
    A custom class representation of an RBNB source object It contains the source name and type (e.g.
    SegaServerObject
    This helper class is used to store info returned from a SQL database containing valid servers.
    XYDataPointObject
    A generic key/value class used for a few different functions but was written to store RBNB data where x is the timestamp and y is the datapoint.
